                <td class="border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 px-3 py-2">3억원 초과</td>
                <td class="border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 px-3 py-2">0.4%</td>
                <td class="border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 px-3 py-2">57만원 + 초과분의 0.4%</td>
